title: 'Star Awakens' Trailer Debuts - Watch Now!
text: The brand new Star Wars: The Force Awakens trailer just debuted during Monday Night Football and it’s everything we’ve been waiting for! The seventh episode in the Star Wars series stars John Boyega, Daisy Ridley, Adam Driver, Oscar Isaac, Andy Serkis, Lupita Nyong’o, Gwendoline Christie, Domhnall Gleeson, Pip Anderson, and Max von Sydow alongside returning [...] »
